strapiEvent.name: FREE Career Event Sponsored by Insight Global
strapiEvent.location: Washington County Fairgrounds, located at 2537 N McConnell Ave, Fayetteville, AR 72704
strapiEvent.description:
Do you have career goals? Let our experts help boost your career confidence by building a resume, practicing those interview skills, providing free headshots, and connecting you with employers through our FREE Mobile Career Center event.


Open to everyone who dreams of a better job! We’ll help you turn your experience and skills into powerful career-building tools. It’s your time to shine! Complimentary childcare and food will be available, and support will be provided for Spanish speakers and the hearing and physically impaired. 


Seats are limited, register today at http://www.insightglobal.com/careerstart.
